  <summary>3/12/1998--Introduced.
Prohibits: (1) any person who is engaged in the production of a movie for commercial viewing from having any arrangement with a tobacco company under which such person is paid to have a tobacco product featured in the movie; and (2) such a movie from being distributed in interstate commerce.</summary>
